
  ===========================================
  = HwGallery - simple image gallery in PHP =
  ===========================================

  version 0.85

Requirements
------------

- PHP version 5
- PHP has to have write rights to directory "thumbs"

Installation
------------

1. Put files in this archive to the server by FTP.
2. Put images into directory photos. You can use subfolders, but their names
   may be only combination of alphanumeric chars and - symbol.
3. Set proper write rights to the directory "thumbs".

Package description
-------------------

- [photos]: directory pro images
  - [skins]: directory for skins (templates) 
    - [default_en]: default template (English version) 
      - background.gif, folder.gif, next.gif, prev.gif: images for
        default template
      - folder_view.tpl: HTML template for display of folder content
      - image_view.tpl: HTML template for display of image 
      - skin.properties: the only mandatory file of template with settings
      - styles.css: styles for default template
    - [default_cs]: default template (Czech version)
      - ... 
- [thumbs]: directory for saving of automatically generated thumbails
- hw_gallery.php: script with class HwGallery (used for generating of
  gallery)
- hw_gallery.properties - main gallery settings
- hw_ini_file.php: auxiliary script with class for properties files parsing
- index.php - basic simple script for display of gallery

License
-------

Whole package is completely for free even for commercial use but there is
one requirement: there have to be links to my homepage (http://tomashula.cz) and
gallery page (http://tomashula.cz/index.php?tid=php-jednoducha-galerie) on every
page of applied gallery.